item.title: CVE-2023-24958|2024-08-02T11:11:43.200Z -- ibm -- virtualization%20engine%20ts7700
item.description: A vulnerability in the IBM TS7700 Management Interface 8.51.2.12, 8.52.200.111, 8.52.102.13, and 8.53.0.63 could allow an authenticated user to submit a specially crafted URL leading to privilege escalation and remote code execution. IBM X-Force ID: 246320.
